  "text": "HomeCareersBring all of your skin-care questions and tune in on Monday, Dec. 9.Steph here. I'm so excited to share that I'll be joining Kristen Noel Crawley, founder of skin-care brand KNC Beauty, on The Fashionista Network. But here's the best part: I want you to join me! It's your opportunity to interact live with us, ask questions and be a part of the show.We'll discuss how Crawley has steadily grown KNC Beauty since its 2016 launch amid an ever-changing beauty industry. We'll also dive into KNC's upcoming launches, how she's navigating TikTok's growing importance, what's in store for the brand's future and her insights into the skin-care business.This conversation will be publicly accessible (no paywall!) on The Fashionista Network powered by interactive media platform Fireside, and you'll get the chance to participate and join the stage with video to ask questions directly. Learn more about The Fashionista Network here.Scroll to ContinueRecommended ArticlesYou don't want to miss this show on Monday, Dec. 9 at 10 a.m. PT/1 p.m. ET. Sign up for free access now (and don't forget to become a member to access all of our members-only shows and perks as well).Homepage photo: Courtesy of KNC BeautyTune into The Fashionista Network to join the conversation with fashion and beauty industry leaders. Sign up here.Subscribe to Our Newsletter",
